text:
Since the beginning, I always related myself to you.
We guys came from rural background, worked our ass off to withstand that wind .
I have just some lines to say for u:

Jab ek din saare kaam pure kar do, ghar valo ke liye kuch paise bhi juta do .
Jab ek din vo jimmedaari apne kandhe se hat jae,
To ek lambi saans lena , aur apna kandha thap thapana.
Aur phir kadam badhana, ek naye sire ki aur , ek nayi manjil, ek naya raasta aur ek naya Kamboj.

#yaaranemule
author: Rohit  Lambora

text:
I have seen you crying, laughing, dancing and what not !
Cheers to all those memories starting from :
>> DMID ka Randaap, NCC ka saath, Swimming krke weightloss karne ka asfal prayas;
Rooftop ka rejection, और  अंत मे महादेव का प्रसाद !!

Chal nikal laude !
author: Rohit  Lambora
